OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777471867
OL,3,CMan due in court charged with murder
OL,4,Cand attempted murder following stabbing
OL,6,FA man has been charged in connection
OL,7,Fwith the death of a 37-year-old man in
OL,8,FBrighton.
OL,10,FPolice were called to reports of a
OL,11,Ffight taking place inside a property
OL,12,Fin Regency Square at around 2:10am on
OL,13,FSunday 26 April.
OL,15,FTwo men were found with stab injuries.
OL,17,FOne man, now formally identified as
OL,18,FTio Day, was pronounced dead at the
OL,19,Fscene. His next of kin have been
OL,20,Finformed and are being supported by
OL,21,Fspecially trained officers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
