FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777471867
OL,3,CMan due in court charged with murder
OL,4,Cand attempted murder following stabbing
OL,6,FThe second man, in his 30s, was taken
OL,7,Fto hospital for treatment.
OL,9,FOfficers went to a nearby hotel
OL,10,Ffollowing reports of a man entering
OL,11,Fthe reception and showing concerning
OL,12,Fbehaviour.
OL,14,FDaniel Bassett, of no fixed address,
OL,15,Fwas arrested in connection with the
OL,16,Fincident and taken to custody.
OL,18,FOn Tuesday 28 April, he was charged
OL,19,Fwith murder and attempted murder.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
