PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777471867
OL,3,CMan due in court charged with murder
OL,4,Cand attempted murder following stabbing
OL,6,FBassett has been remanded to appear
OL,7,Fbefore Brighton Magistrates' Court on
OL,8,FWednesday 29 April.
OL,10,FBrighton and Hove Chief Superintendent
OL,11,FAdam Hays said: "Our thoughts are with
OL,12,FTio's family and friends at this very
OL,13,Fdifficult time.
OL,15,F"Tragic incidents like this have
OL,16,Fsignificant consequences. Lives are
OL,17,Flost or changed forever, families are
OL,18,Fleft grieving, and entire communities
OL,19,Fare affected.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
